    {
      "id": "6a1766f0000000000029a4ce",
      "text": "[***** [アセチルコリン]]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779918575,
      "updated": 1779919036
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1766fb000000000029a4d1",
      "text": "\t[*** [アセチルコリン]] (ACh)：2-acetyloxyethyl(trimethyl)azanium",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779918587,
      "updated": 1779919041
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176712000000000029a4d4",
      "text": " \t[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/アセチルコリン アセチルコリン]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779918611,
      "updated": 1779918616
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176707000000000029a4d2",
      "text": " \t[https://gyazo.com/e6bdd8ed7322949fee63440e9c9709af][https://gyazo.com/5e07808d0e35bb8cd32e0d34506a85ad][https://gyazo.com/beb6d58e79fd71f934bdfe5ccf623972]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779918598,
      "updated": 1779918756
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176885000000000029a4d7",
      "text": " \t[酢酸]（[アセチル酸]）と[コリン]の[脱水縮合]物",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779918981,
      "updated": 1779919125
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176b71000000000029a4f1",
      "text": " \t[酵素][コリンアセチルトランスフェラーゼ]（ChAT）によって[コリン]と[アセチルコエンザイムA]（[アセチルCoA]）から作られる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779919729,
      "updated": 1779919774
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176710000000000029a4d3",
      "text": "\t\t[酵素][アセチルコリンエステラーゼ]（AChE）の作用で[コリン]と[酢酸]に[加水分解]、除去される。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779918608,
      "updated": 1779919652
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176895000000000029a4d8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779918997,
      "updated": 1779918997
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1766f4000000000029a4cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779918580,
      "updated": 1779918580
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176972000000000029a4da",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779919218,
      "updated": 1779919218
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176973000000000029a4db",
      "text": "[***** [モノアミン]類]：[アミノ基]を1つだけ含む[神経伝達物質]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779919219,
      "updated": 1779922770
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176987000000000029a4dc",
      "text": " [フェニルアラニン]、[チロシン]より合成（[合成経路]で[カテコールアミン]を経由）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779919238,
      "updated": 1779919340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176a07000000000029a4ea",
      "text": " \t前提",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779919367,
      "updated": 1779919372
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176a0c000000000029a4eb",
      "text": " \t\t[フェニルアラニン](Phe, F)：2-Amino-3-phenylpropanoic acid",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779919372,
      "updated": 1779919916
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176bec000000000029a4f2",
      "text": " \t\t\t[コドン]：UUU、UUC",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779919852,
      "updated": 1779919896
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176bf6000000000029a4f3",
      "text": " \t\t\t[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/フェニルアラニン フェニルアラニン]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779919861,
      "updated": 1779919861
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176cb5000000000029a4fb",
      "text": " \t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/92e01fba6a358274e371bcf68cf5b481][https://gyazo.com/bf9b8d62e0afaa3d1921c80ab3412e12]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779920053,
      "updated": 1779920060
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176a0f000000000029a4ec",
      "text": "  \t\t動物は[フェニルアラニン]を体内で作り出すことができない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779919374,
      "updated": 1779920634
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176d22000000000029a4ff",
      "text": "  \t\tL-[フェニルアラニン]は生体内で L-[チロシン]に変換され、さらに L-[ドーパ]となる。これがさらに[ドーパミン]や[ノルアドレナリン]、[アドレナリン]へと誘導される。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779920162,
      "updated": 1779920162
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176fd8000000000029a50f",
      "text": "  \t\t\tL-[ドーパ]：(S)-2-Amino-3-(3,4-dihydroxyphenyl)propanoic acid",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779920856,
      "updated": 1779921032
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176ff2000000000029a512",
      "text": "   \t\t\t[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/L-DOPA L-DOPA]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779920882,
      "updated": 1779921060
    },
    {
      "id": "6a177001000000000029a513",
      "text": "   \t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/dd52d8d74d5579c80bf572178d2935b6][https://gyazo.com/9e089fa762f998891fdafe0cd37cf1fe]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779920897,
      "updated": 1779920909
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176ce2000000000029a4fe",
      "text": " \t\t[チロシン](Tyr, Y)：2-Amino-3-(4-hydroxyphenyl)propanoic acid",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779920097,
      "updated": 1779920118
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176c12000000000029a4f4",
      "text": " \t\t\t[コドン]：UAU、UAC",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779919890,
      "updated": 1779919993
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176c66000000000029a4f6",
      "text": " \t\t\t[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/チロシン チロシン]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779919974,
      "updated": 1779919979
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176c84000000000029a4f7",
      "text": " \t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/342277b68b66f1715f349cd4221259df][https://gyazo.com/26e45c14b191dd0efd22d06784b2373f][https://gyazo.com/908d880f3f7e92f014d23096e656c6ef]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779920004,
      "updated": 1779920041
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176a12000000000029a4ed",
      "text": " \t\t[カテコールアミン]：[カテコール]と[アミン]を有する化合物",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779919377,
      "updated": 1779920340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a176f99000000000029a509",
